   $ [[System.AdminToolsCategory.TOPICKEY]] : List of tools available to the Foswiki administrator
   $ [[System.UserDocumentationCategory.TOPICKEY]] : List of documents for the everyday user from beginner to advanced user
   $ [[System.UserToolsCategory.TOPICKEY]] :  List of tools the user may need for setting and resetting passwords, changing email address etc.
